window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jamie Beckett was just another overworked nobody. Dead end job, crappy apartment, and no way out.</b><br> <br> Then he met the bleeding elf in the alley.</p> <p>Turns out Jamie is a Leasher. One of a rare few born with the ability to bond powerful beings to himself. When he forms his first bond with the beautiful, dagger wielding elf, Lilly, Jamie gets dragged into a divine game where power and survival are all tangled up.</p> <p>With assassins on his trail, beautiful women piling into his life, and a magical power he barely understands, Jamie will have to learn fast or lose everything.</p> <p><b>Spicy, sharp-witted, and fueled by raw magical chemistry, </b><b><i>First Leash</i></b><b> is a fantasy adventure full of dangerous women, sarcastic banter, and unexpected heart.</b></p>"; 
